#import "../fragments/full-answer.graphql"

mutation answerCreate(
  $displayValue: String!
  $value: String!
  $valueType: AnswerValueTypeOptions!
  $riskAdjustmentType: RiskAdjustmentTypeOptions
  $inSummary: Boolean
  $summaryText: String
  $questionId: String!
  $order: Int!
) {
  answerCreate(input: {
    displayValue: $displayValue
    value: $value
    valueType: $valueType
    riskAdjustmentType: $riskAdjustmentType
    inSummary: $inSummary
    summaryText: $summaryText
    questionId: $questionId
    order: $order
  }) {
    ...FullAnswer
  }
}

mutation answerEdit(
  $answerId: String!
  $displayValue: String
  $value: String
  $valueType: AnswerValueTypeOptions
  $riskAdjustmentType: RiskAdjustmentTypeOptions
  $inSummary: Boolean
  $summaryText: String
  $order: Int
) {
  answerEdit(input: {
    answerId: $answerId
    displayValue: $displayValue
    value: $value
    valueType: $valueType
    riskAdjustmentType: $riskAdjustmentType
    inSummary: $inSummary
    summaryText: $summaryText
    order: $order
  }) {
    ...FullAnswer
  }
}

source.body:
#import "../fragments/short-patient.graphql"

mutation patientEdit(
  $patientId: String!
  $firstName: String
  $middleName: String
  $lastName: String
  $dateOfBirth: String
  $gender: String
  $zip: Int
  $language: String
  $consentToCall: Boolean
  $consentToText: Boolean
) {
  patientEdit(input: {
    patientId: $patientId,
    firstName: $firstName,
    middleName: $middleName,
    lastName: $lastName,
    dateOfBirth: $dateOfBirth,
    gender: $gender,
    zip: $zip,
    language: $language,
    consentToCall: $consentToCall,
    consentToText: $consentToText,
   }) {
    ...ShortPatient
  }
}

#import "../fragments/short-patient.graphql"

mutation patientSetup(
  $homeClinicId: String!
  $firstName: String!
  $middleName: String
  $lastName: String!
  $dateOfBirth: String!
  $gender: String!
  $maritalStatus: String!
  $race: String!
  $zip: Int!
  $ssn: String!
  $language: String!
  $email: String
  $homePhone: String
  $mobilePhone: String
  $consentToCall: Boolean!
  $consentToText: Boolean!
  $issueDate: String
  $expirationDate: String
  $insuranceType: String
  $patientRelationshipToPolicyHolder: String
  $memberId: String
  $policyGroupNumber: String
) {
  patientSetup(input: {
    firstName: $firstName,
    middleName: $middleName,
    lastName: $lastName,
    dateOfBirth: $dateOfBirth,
    gender: $gender,
    zip: $zip,
    homeClinicId: $homeClinicId,
    race: $race,
    ssn: $ssn,
    language: $language,
    maritalStatus: $maritalStatus,
    email: $email,
    homePhone: $homePhone,
    mobilePhone: $mobilePhone,
    consentToCall: $consentToCall,
    consentToText: $consentToText,
    issueDate: $issueDate,
    expirationDate: $expirationDate,
    insuranceType: $insuranceType,
    patientRelationshipToPolicyHolder: $patientRelationshipToPolicyHolder,
    memberId: $memberId,
    policyGroupNumber: $policyGroupNumber,
   }) {
    ...ShortPatient
  }
}
